title: Inconsistent name spelling
body:
The repo and other references use SmuggleSheild, but the readme starts with "*SmuggleShield* is an experimental browser extension." The latter is the spelling I'd expect.
Which spelling is intended, shield or sheild?
author: ShaddyDC

comments.body: Thank you, indeed its a typo it should be "SmuggleSheild"
